dc.title: Representative Michael McCaul, Proudly Serving the People of the 10th District of Texas
dc.description: Congressman Michael McCaul represents Texas'10th District in the United States Congress. The 10th Congressional District of Texas stretches across 8 counties from Austin to the Houston suburbs, and includes Austin, Bastrop, Burleson, Harris, Lee, Travis, Washington and Waller Counties.
